			<td class="print">
				For the developer:<br />
<br />
Deleted .gitattributes file, fixed .gitignore, added tomcat maven plugin (I will explain why in the developer guide soon), moved generated code to maven &quot;target&quot; directory (maven standard practices), made GWT target directory to store GWT temporary files (preventing compilation to fill hard-drive and fail miserably).<br />
<br />
For the release manager (aka myself):<br />
<br />
Declared license maven plugin to automatically add license header on all files (I will call it at each release to make sure all files have the expected header and did it on the current repository). Created Jenkins build (and mentioned it in POM), there (will add the URL in the wiki soon) :<br />
<br />
<a href="http://ci.codelutin.com/jenkins/job/sigmah-ci/">http://ci.codelutin.com/jenkins/job/sigmah-ci/</a> [<a href="http://ci.codelutin.com/jenkins/job/sigmah-ci/" target="_blank">^</a>]<br />
<br />
More to come!			</td>
